description.ar: Discover Bayview by Address Resorts at Emaar Beachfront, and experience the panoramic views, luxury interiors, and amenities. Visit us online for more info. Ethereal waves adorn stylishly crafted façades reflecting the Arabian Gulf’s rippling waters. A luxury vocabulary inspired by the splendour and glamour of Dubai, translated in the smallest details, inside and out. Penthouses are the crowning achievements of richly rewarding lives. Placed at the very top of the gracefully designed towers, you will find the highest heights of Emaar Beachfront’s lifestyle. The Bayview by Address Resorts 5-bedroom penthouses are the epitome of premier sky-rise living, a canvas of dazzling opulence on the Arabian Gulf's horizon. Four unique penthouse residences defy all expectations with 360-degree views and the design of contemporary beach estates. The finest interiors and materials blend flawlessly with elegant design, to create a haven for ultimate luxury in the ultimate destination.

description.ar: EMAAR Beachfront offers a luxurious, private island lifestyle at Dubai Harbour. This exclusive, gated community provides unparalleled access to the city’s premier attractions, including world-class malls, gourmet restaurants, and prestigious yacht clubs. It's an off-plan development by Emaar Properties, strategically located near Sheikh Zayed Road, ensuring a seamless commute to all parts of Dubai. Awaken your senses with every breath, as you redefine your premium lifestyle, overlooking the majestic Arabian Gulf at Emaar Beachfront. Emaar Beachfront brings world-class shopping and entertainment right to your doorstep, part of this meticulously planned off-plan development by Emaar Properties. Imagine waking up to the soothing sounds of the sea every morning and coming home to pristine white sand beaches. This masterfully planned development caters to every aspect of premium living, with proximity to prestigious yacht clubs, gourmet restaurants, and the best shopping malls Dubai has to offer, including those in Palm Jumeirah and Dubai Marina. Whether it's a relaxing day at the beach or a vibrant night out, Emaar Beachfront promises a lifestyle of unparalleled luxury and convenience in one of Dubai's most sought-after neighbourhoods.

description.ar: Downtown Dubai, our flagship mega-development, aptly named The Centre of Now, spans two of the most prestigious square kilometres in the city. Positioned between Sheikh Zayed Road and Financial Centre Road, this dynamic hub has driven the economy and cemented Dubai’s reputation as a true global icon. At the heart of the emirate, Downtown Dubai offers a metropolitan lifestyle surrounded by world-class landmarks, entertainment, and glamour. One of the key attractions in the area is Dubai Mall, the world’s largest shopping mall, offering an unrivalled selection of retail and dining options. Properties in Downtown Dubai represent the pinnacle of luxury living, with a skyline dominated by contemporary high-rise residences, complemented by world-class amenities and a thriving cultural scene. From sleek condominiums with panoramic views of the iconic skyline to elegant townhouses nestled along tree-lined avenues, each home exudes sophistication and style. With premium amenities such as private pools, state-of-the-art fitness centres, and exclusive concierge services, these properties elevate the concept of urban living to new heights. Whether seeking a cosmopolitan penthouse or a family-friendly retreat, Downtown Dubai offers an unmatched opportunity to experience the epitome of opulent city living.

description.ar: Downtown Dubai, our flagship mega-development, aptly named The Centre of Now, spans two of the most prestigious square kilometres in the city. Positioned between Sheikh Zayed Road and Financial Centre Road, this dynamic hub has driven the economy and cemented Dubai’s reputation as a true global icon. At the heart of the emirate, Downtown Dubai offers a metropolitan lifestyle surrounded by world-class landmarks, entertainment, and glamour. One of the key attractions in the area is Dubai Mall, the world’s largest shopping mall, offering an unrivalled selection of retail and dining options. Properties in Downtown Dubai represent the pinnacle of luxury living, with a skyline dominated by contemporary high-rise residences, complemented by world-class amenities and a thriving cultural scene. From sleek condominiums with panoramic views of the iconic skyline to elegant townhouses nestled along tree-lined avenues, each home exudes sophistication and style. With premium amenities such as private pools, state-of-the-art fitness centres, and exclusive concierge services, these properties elevate the concept of urban living to new heights. Whether seeking a cosmopolitan penthouse or a family-friendly retreat, Downtown Dubai offers an unmatched opportunity to experience the epitome of opulent city living.

Its well-designed infrastructure ensures connectivity, and a 3.5-kilometer water canal with dual sea access, makes it a top sailing destination. Emaar’s vision for Dubai Marina combines luxury with convenience, offering iconic residences that capture the vibrancy of waterfront living and city energy. description.ar: تعد دبي مارينا معلماً نابضاً بالحياة يجسد جاذبية دبي العالمية. كواحدة من أكبر المجتمعات المائية وأكثرها شهرة في المنطقة، تقدم أسلوب حياة مستوحى من الريفيرا، يمزج بين التصميم المعاصر ولمسة من الأناقة. مع رحلات اليخوت والرياضات المائية والمقاهي في الهواء الطلق، يمكن للمقيمين والزوار الانغماس في أجواء المرسى المفعمة بالحيوية وتجربة نمط حياة لا مثيل له. يضم المجتمع مساكن فاخرة، من الشقق على الواجهة البحرية إلى البنتهاوس مع إطلالات شاملة على المرسى وأفق المدينة، وهي مثالية للعائلات والمهنيين والمستثمرين الباحثين عن حياة حضرية راقية. من خلال عرض الهندسة المعمارية الحديثة والمساكن الواسعة، أصبحت دبي مارينا مثالاً للمعيشة الراقية. تضمن بنيتها التحتية المصممة جيدًا الاتصال، وقناة مائية بطول 3.5 كيلومتر مع وصول مزدوج إلى البحر، مما يجعلها وجهة رئيسية للإبحار. تجمع رؤية إعمار لدبي مارينا بين الفخامة والراحة، حيث تقدم مساكن مميزة تجسد حيوية الحياة على الواجهة البحرية وطاقة المدينة. إنها لا توفر مجرد منزل، بل طريقة حياة راقية.

description.ar: اكتشف الحياة الفاخرة في عنوان ريزيدنسز في جزيرة المرجان، رأس الخيمة. استكشف العقارات الرائعة التي توفر الراحة والأناقة والإطلالات الخلابة. انغمس في أسلوب حياة مثالي على جزيرة محاطة بأفق الإمارات العربية المتحدة المهيب وبحر العرب الفيروزي. هنا، يُعاد تعريف الفخامة: ملاذ هادئ مع كل وسائل الراحة الحديثة على عتبة داركم. غروب الشمس المذهل والصباحات المليئة بالمناظر الخلابة للبحر والمناظر الطبيعية. شواطئ خاصة واسعة ومناظر طبيعية خضراء ومسابح لا متناهية تمتزج مع المياه. سيمفونية من وسائل الراحة الفاخرة لتستمتع بها. إنه مكان يتم فيه تنسيق كل لحظة لتقديم تجربة معيشية لا مثيل لها، حيث يجسد كل تفصيل وعدًا بحياة جيدة. جرب التوازن المثالي بين الفخامة الحديثة والجمال الهادئ في عنوان ريزيدنسز جزيرة المرجان، وهو ملاذ هادئ يقع في جزيرة فيو الخلابة في رأس الخيمة. استمتع بكل يوم مع إطلالات بحرية رائعة ومناظر طبيعية هادئة واسترخِ في المساء مع غروب الشمس المذهل. تتميز هذه الوجهة الفاخرة بشواطئ واسعة ومساحات خضراء نابضة بالحياة ومسابح لا متناهية مدهشة تمتزج مع المياه الزرقاء الصافية. استمتع بمجموعة من وسائل الراحة من الدرجة الأولى المصممة لراحتك ومتعتك. يعكس كل جانب من جوانب هذا المشروع التزامًا بأسلوب حياة من الرقي والأناقة.

Every residence is brought to life with intricate detail and striking expression, offering a marina living experience beyond the ordinary. Rashid Yachts & Marina redefines Dubai’s seafront coastal legacy — a realm of fearless ambition and infinite discovery.

description.ar: Dubai Marina is a vibrant landmark that embodies Dubai’s cosmopolitan allure. As one of the region’s largest and most iconic waterfront communities, it introduces a Riviera-inspired lifestyle, blending contemporary design with a touch of elegance. With yacht cruises, water sports, and alfresco cafes, residents and visitors can immerse themselves in marina’s lively atmosphere and unparalleled lifestyle experience. The community features luxury residences, from waterfront apartments to penthouses with sweeping marina and skyline views, ideal for families, professionals, and investors seeking refined urban living. Showcasing modern architecture and expansive residences, Dubai Marina has become the epitome of upscale living. Its well-designed infrastructure ensures connectivity, and a 3.5-kilometer water canal with dual sea access, makes it a top sailing destination. Emaar’s vision for Dubai Marina combines luxury with convenience, offering iconic residences that capture the vibrancy of waterfront living and city energy. It provides not just a home, but an elevated way of life.
